title: Burlingame Townhome
posting_body: ['This quiet 2 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom condo is two blocks from Burlingame Avenue.', 'It sits away from the street with gated access to two parking spots, a patio garden and plenty of space to enjoy peace and quiet.', '*Secure gated property.', '*Two level unit with one shared wall.', '*2 Master bedrooms upstairs each with their own bathroom, balcony and vaulted ceilings.', '*A half bath downstairs', '*Fireplace', '*Wetbar', '*Dining room off the kitchen.', '*Cozy patio with a little garden.', '*Marble and hardwood floors downstairs.', '*Carpeted bedrooms upstairs.', '*Washer Dryer in unit.', '*Skylights upstairs.', '*Plenty of closet space.', '*An attic to store decorations and boxes.', '*Garage has a 100 sq ft storage unit.', '*2 Secure parking spots with easy access to your front door.', '*Large refrigerator and freezer.', '*Large pantry in kitchen', '*Direct access to common area with space for a garden.', '*It has a walk score of 93!', '*Two blocks from Burlingame Avenue', "*Lots of questions about proximity to the train but it's not loud at all.", 'Minimum year lease.', 'Deposit is one month rent.', 'OWNER covers trash, sewer, water.', 'RENTER covers gas, electric.', 'This unit will be available after August 3, 2022.']
